  <h4>Progressive uses of <mark>faighnich</mark></h4>
  <p>When used progressively, <strong>(bi) a’ faighneachd</strong> generally carries the extended meaning <en>ask oneself, wonder</en>.</p> 
  <p>For example, <mark>tha mi a’ faighneachd ciamar a tha i</mark> <en>I wonder how she is</en>. <boxlink ref="#wonder"/></p>

